data.title: Category:Supported Games
data.meta_description: This category is for games that are supported by ScummVM. There is also a category for unsupported games.
data.text:
This category is for games that are supported by ScummVM. There is also a category for unsupported games.

This category only includes games that have their own wiki page. Due to the huge number of games, many GLK and AGS games are not present.

For these engines, see Engines/Glk and AGS/Games.
